{"tw": {"3439830": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "終末的死鬥場少女", "steam_appid": 3439830, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.poster.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.webm?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.mp4?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>●概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為一名技巧高超的槍手，蕾歐娜為了洗刷罪名，在法律邊緣遊走。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/87d5351b2905e2d8447d908bb70b153b.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，她遇見了神秘的亞人「露莉」，並被說服參加了死鬥場的鬥技大賽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大賽的獎品是赦免過去所有的罪行。為了贏得自由，蕾歐娜必須依靠她的力量、策略與智慧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能否智取所有對手，成為無可爭議的冠軍？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●養成系統<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・執行各種工作來提升能力值，同時賺取金錢。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・有時需要休息來恢復健康度，並從戰鬥帶來的負面狀態中恢復。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・可以花錢在城市裡購物或接受專門的戰鬥訓練。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●戰鬥系統</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・採用 1 對 1 的戰術決鬥模式。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・戰鬥前準備好技能牌組，並根據對手的行動來決定主角的行動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・主角的技能各自設定了消耗值，若消耗值不足，技能便無法發動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・能看穿敵方行動的程度，取決於主角的預判能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・迅速決定主角的行動、或是以零傷害通過回合等行動，會提升主角的情緒值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　情緒值上升後，主角將進入「狂熱射擊」狀態，攻擊力會大幅提升。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●伶牙俐齒模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蕾歐娜非常善於言辭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在劇情中，她會用她那巧妙的辯論技巧來進行各種協商與博弈。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在互動過程中，她的話語有機會開創新的機遇、揭露隱藏的情報，或引導至意想不到的挑戰。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●內容詳情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・基本HCG圖33張（含Live2D H場景）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・基本立繪H圖7張 x 7套服裝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*遊戲內部皆為無碼版本*</h2>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.poster.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.webm?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/da24c415f93f7d8a4082383500069e48.mp4?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>●概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為一名技巧高超的槍手，蕾歐娜為了洗刷罪名，在法律邊緣遊走。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/87d5351b2905e2d8447d908bb70b153b.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，她遇見了神秘的亞人「露莉」，並被說服參加了死鬥場的鬥技大賽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大賽的獎品是赦免過去所有的罪行。為了贏得自由，蕾歐娜必須依靠她的力量、策略與智慧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能否智取所有對手，成為無可爭議的冠軍？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●養成系統<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・執行各種工作來提升能力值，同時賺取金錢。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・有時需要休息來恢復健康度，並從戰鬥帶來的負面狀態中恢復。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・可以花錢在城市裡購物或接受專門的戰鬥訓練。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●戰鬥系統</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・採用 1 對 1 的戰術決鬥模式。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・戰鬥前準備好技能牌組，並根據對手的行動來決定主角的行動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・主角的技能各自設定了消耗值，若消耗值不足，技能便無法發動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・能看穿敵方行動的程度，取決於主角的預判能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・迅速決定主角的行動、或是以零傷害通過回合等行動，會提升主角的情緒值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　情緒值上升後，主角將進入「狂熱射擊」狀態，攻擊力會大幅提升。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●伶牙俐齒模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蕾歐娜非常善於言辭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在劇情中，她會用她那巧妙的辯論技巧來進行各種協商與博弈。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在互動過程中，她的話語有機會開創新的機遇、揭露隱藏的情報，或引導至意想不到的挑戰。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >●內容詳情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・基本HCG圖33張（含Live2D H場景）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・基本立繪H圖7張 x 7套服裝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*遊戲內部皆為無碼版本*</h2>", "short_description": "槍手蕾歐娜為贏得自由，參加了死鬥場的致命賽事。 勝利意味著所有罪狀一筆勾銷，但獲勝不能只憑火力。 她必須依靠力量、策略與智慧戰勝每一位對手。 她能否征服鬥技場，奪回自己的未來？", "supported_languages": "日文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1770950004", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/3e76eb78be4f800adff6dd03b0c3049018a31460/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1770950004", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/3e76eb78be4f800adff6dd03b0c3049018a31460/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1770950004", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel® Core™ 2 Duo E6600 or AMD Phenom™ X3 8750<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Intel Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 12 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["TLACHTLI"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 24900, "final": 22400, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 249", "final_formatted": "NT$ 224"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}, {"id": "2", "description": "策略"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 2 月 12 日"}}}}, "us": {"3439830": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "DEAD END COLOSSEUM", "steam_appid": 3439830, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/f393beba022bada79aea30ca8928da3d.poster.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/f393beba022bada79aea30ca8928da3d.webm?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/f393beba022bada79aea30ca8928da3d.mp4?t=1770950004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leona, a skilled gunslinger living on the fringes of the law, seeks a chance to clear her nam.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e31baaee9b9f5aa831856352aedf1edd.avif?t=1770950004\" width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, she meets Lurie, a sketchy demi-human, who persuades her to enter the combat tournament held at the Colosseum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The grand prize is a full pardon for all past crimes. To win her freedom, Leona must rely on her strength, strategy, and wit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Leona outsmart her opponents and rise as the undisputed champion?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e6c9ac3f870080fe1715aa00894bffa7.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Perform various jobs to enhance your abilities and earn money.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/802b9381647c7fd2f3be5541aef46832.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Take a break once in a while to restore Health and recover from combat debuffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spend money on gear, items, and specialized combat training. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fight powerful opponents in 1v1 tactical matches.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/2626c291da41de4125eed1ce9b037f61.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Prepare your deck of skills before battle, and select the best moves to counter your enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Each skill has a fixed cost and requires sufficient stats to activate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Accurately predicting the opponent's next move depends on Leona's foresight ability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Quick move selection and successive turns without taking damage will increase Leona's Excitement gauge. A high Excitement level triggers her &quot;Trigger-Happy&quot; mode, boosting her attack power.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/7d431d2e51bf8ba400715ddd60c35947.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leona the Silver-Tongued</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leona can use her sharp wit to negotiate with various characters she meets.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/3f097bbb447c4640eb22ab769cb95c91.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depending on the situation, her words can unlock new opportunities, reveal hidden information, or lead to unexpected challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439830/extras_big/e4b7087bc5b68fa930472d5e05308a8e.avif?t=1770950004 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>H-Content &amp; Features <br>- 33 H-CGs (including Live2D scenes)<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Seven portrait poses x Seven different outfits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >